{"tid":817761,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得以前嘅細路仔好幸福","createTime":"2018-09-13T14:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T18:54:19.000Z","uid":4375,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8943306120ea80cfc15f164c8ba69ee5ad3e5d03","tid":817761,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"人在外面見到啲幼稚園 小學生放學 老豆老母帶佢地去公園坐下玩下<br />\n以前香港啲細路仔都係放學去公園玩 一係返屋企睇卡通片 都叫有返啲童年<br />\n宜家啲細路放學趕住去補習溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573a9f0d33801418f0cf99473d46680ec3c88e52","tid":817761,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"外國*"},{"pid":"ff46ae5d0f7cb4dc439d5dce707ed43bb1e74112","tid":817761,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"幫個小四細路補習，日日放四點去功課班到6點，一星期有兩日再過我度補到8點，返去食完飯又對功課。"},{"pid":"4371a4a732f9f642a7d2df5221644f1db3621d11","tid":817761,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"學生補習根本就戇鳩多舊魚，高中補習都算，小學補習根本就盲目跟風，個細蚊仔只係為咗應付父母，學唔到啲乜。"},{"pid":"76bdafd1dc3f7c3f9e2ad11ded1ea2230dd8bbf2","tid":817761,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4371a4a732f9f642a7d2df5221644f1db3621d11","tid":817761,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"學生補習根本就戇鳩多舊魚，高中補習都算，小學補習根本就盲目跟風，個細蚊仔只係為咗應付父母，學唔到啲乜。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:52:32.000Z","msg":"係啊， 個啲濕鳩補習社只係用黎比你掟個仔入去，等有人幫你睇住<br />\n順便對埋功課咁<br />\n根本學唔到野<br />\n我以前都有去過，其實乜都學唔到 哂時間<br />\n問題係我老母話人地去左成績好好先叫我去<br />\n但人地啲教育方法同我根本唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c2a8461e1565f8573c8a9ba5a90345d9b0b36f","tid":817761,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:54:19.000Z","msg":"宜家細路有得上網，直播，抖音"}]}